{"title":"小兴安岭","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":5,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"小兴安岭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"严辰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打开袖珍本的地图，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我把小兴安岭寻觅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一片不小的空白，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"包涵了什么样的哑谜？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我走进小兴安岭深处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才发现这是个新的天地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无穷无尽的绿色树海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么丰富又那么神奇！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"2"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感谢森林调查队员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一个踏遍了原始森林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给许多山沟取了新的名字："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美溪、蔚蓝、大丰、常青……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感谢地质勘探工作者，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走遍了大大小小的山岭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"揭穿了地下的秘密，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把每一处岩层敲醒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"3"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早晨我登高眺望，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树在云上、云在树上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不见伐木工人在那里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只听得大树伐倒应山响。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜晚我登高眺望天空闪耀着通红的火光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高炉里铁水奔流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高炉边人马喧嚷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"4"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我喜爱兴安岭的民歌："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里的树是摇钱树，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里的山是万宝山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里的河是金银川。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请容许我加上一句："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里的人是英雄汉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正是几十万双勤劳的手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才教荒凉的面貌彻底改观。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}